      "name": "Section 1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "start": 142.54,
          "end": 145.96,
          "text": "Oh hello I'd like to ask about insurance for my car."
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "start": 146.32,
          "end": 151.02,
          "text": "Yes, of course. I'll just take a few details. What's your name?"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "start": 151.72,
          "end": 153.62,
          "text": "Patrick Jones . Example"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "start": 153.62,
          "end": 155.16,
          "text": "And your address?"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "start": 156.28,
          "end": 159.72,
          "text": "It's 27 Bank Road ."
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "start": 159.72,
          "end": 164.24,
          "text": "27 Bank Road. Is that in Greendale?"
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
          "start": 164.24,
          "end": 166.7,
          "text": "And what's your daytime phone number?"
        },
        {
          "id": 8,
          "start": 166.7,
          "end": 171.74,
          "text": "My work number is 730453."
        },
        {
          "id": 9,
          "start": 171.74,
          "end": 175.92,
          "text": "And could I ask what your occupation is?"
        },
        {
          "id": 10,
          "start": 177.18,
          "end": 183.18,
          "text": "OK now a few details about your car What size is the engine?"
        },
        {
          "id": 11,
          "start": 183.18,
          "end": 185.36,
          "text": "It's 1200 ccs."
        },
        {
          "id": 12,
          "start": 219.22,
          "end": 223.02,
          "text": "Thank you and the make and model?"
        },
        {
          "id": 13,
          "start": 223.02,
          "end": 224.5,
          "text": "It's a Hewton Sable."
        },
        {
          "id": 14,
          "start": 289.7,
          "end": 293.36,
          "text": "Could you spell the model name please?"
        },
        {
          "id": 15,
          "start": 293.36,
          "end": 294.6,
          "text": "Yes S-A-B-L-E ."
        },
        {
          "id": 16,
          "start": 294.6,
          "end": 300.06,
          "text": "Ah yes thanks. And when was it made?"
        },
        {
          "id": 17,
          "start": 300.88,
          "end": 304.54,
          "text": "Lovely right I presume you've had a previous insurer?"
        },
        {
          "id": 18,
          "start": 304.54,
          "end": 308.88,
          "text": "Right we need to know the name of the company."
        },
        {
          "id": 19,
          "start": 308.88,
          "end": 310.06,
          "text": "Yes it was Northern Star ."
        },
        {
          "id": 20,
          "start": 410.54,
          "end": 413.3,
          "text": "Thank you, and have you made any insurance claims in the last five years?"
        },
        {
          "id": 21,
          "start": 413.3,
          "end": 415.26,
          "text": "Yes one in 1999."
        },
        {
          "id": 22,
          "start": 415.26,
          "end": 417.22,
          "text": "And what was the problem?"
        },
        {
          "id": 23,
          "start": 417.22,
          "end": 419.18,
          "text": "It was stolen but"
        },
        {
          "id": 24,
          "start": 419.18,
          "end": 421.14,
          "text": "That's line, Mr Jones that's all we need to know at the moment"
        },
        {
          "id": 25,
          "start": 421.14,
          "end": 423.1,
          "text": "And will there be any other named drivers?"
        },
        {
          "id": 26,
          "start": 423.1,
          "end": 425.06,
          "text": "Just the one"
        },
        {
          "id": 27,
          "start": 425.06,
          "end": 427.02,
          "text": "And his name?"
        },
        {
          "id": 28,
          "start": 427.02,
          "end": 428.98,
          "text": "Simon Paynter."
        },
        {
          "id": 29,
          "start": 428.98,
          "end": 430.94,
          "text": "Could you spell the surname please?"
        },
        {
          "id": 30,
          "start": 430.94,
          "end": 432.9,
          "text": "P-A-Y-N-T-E-R ."
        },
        {
          "id": 31,
          "start": 432.9,
          "end": 434.86,
          "text": "OK thank you And what relationship is he to you?"
        },
        {
          "id": 32,
          "start": 434.86,
          "end": 436.81,
          "text": "He's my brother-in-law ."
        },
        {
          "id": 33,
          "start": 436.81,
          "end": 438.77,
          "text": "And what will you or Mr Paynter be using the car for?"
        },
        {
          "id": 34,
          "start": 438.77,
          "end": 440.73,
          "text": "Well mainly for social use"
        },
        {
          "id": 35,
          "start": 440.73,
          "end": 442.69,
          "text": "Social use (murmuring). Will you be using it to travel to work ?"
        },
        {
          "id": 36,
          "start": 442.69,
          "end": 444.65,
          "text": "Yes sometimes."
        },
        {
          "id": 37,
          "start": 444.65,
          "end": 446.61,
          "text": "Anything else?"
        },
        {
          "id": 38,
          "start": 446.61,
          "end": 448.57,
          "text": "No. That's it"
        },
        {
          "id": 39,
          "start": 448.57,
          "end": 450.53,
          "text": "And finally when would you like to start the insurance?"
        },
        {
          "id": 40,
          "start": 450.53,
          "end": 452.49,
          "text": "I'll need it from the 31st of January."
        },
        {
          "id": 41,
          "start": 452.49,
          "end": 454.45,
          "text": "Right Mr Jones I'm getting a couple of quotes coming up on the computer now and the best bet looks like being with a company called Red Flag ."
        },
        {
          "id": 42,
          "start": 454.45,
          "end": 456.41,
          "text": "And that comes out at $ 450 per year"
        },
        {
          "id": 43,
          "start": 456.41,
          "end": 458.37,
          "text": "Well that seems OK it's quite a bit lower than I've been paying up to now"
        },
        {
          "id": 44,
          "start": 458.37,
          "end": 460.33,
          "text": "Great so would you like me to go ahead with that?"
        },
        {
          "id": 45,
          "start": 460.33,
          "end": 462.29,
          "text": "Sure why not?"
        },
        {
          "id": 46,
          "start": 462.29,
          "end": 464.25,
          "text": "How would you like to pay?"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
